{"tid":1384911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［軍糧］有人真係唔食飯，痴線架","createTime":"2019-07-30T03:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:25:42.000Z","uid":274452,"like":88,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"23ecd799d6f8ab39f9ac45e4255e9261ec7116f4","tid":1384911,"uid":274452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:23:11.000Z","msg":"由69開始至今<br />\n示威都未有一個完結既跡象，証明呢個運動係會持續而且持久咁走落去，直到政府唔再龜縮，肯正面回應香港人為止<br />\n長時間既鬥爭係好消磨意志，消磨金錢<br />\n前線既好多都係學生，未有經濟能力，犧牲去做part time既時間，買完裝備可能連飯錢都冇<br />\n我見過唔少數既學生真係唔食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人話請食飯，但唔係個個都唔介意比人請<br />\n佢地都個覺得唔好意思，甚至好多都係自己一個出去，一個人更加唔好意思<br />\n雖然話遊行示威唔係玩，但一個人完結後，無奈地真係會有一種孤獨感<br />\n所以為左凝聚番一班年輕人，會搵支持反修例，示威者既餐廳去接受餐卷。<br />\n咁重點黎啦，餐卷係點黎架呢？<br />\n就係靠一班捐贈者，每50蚊=1餐卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁又有人會話，屌你點派呀？點分到佢係咪真係有份示威？<br />\n咁每一次有示威就會係示威區擺站，有去都知通常前線後小小都會有物資站，就係物資站附近擺，有需要既手足都可以黎拎，帶哂口罩唔駛怕唔好意思，你地值得大家既支持同鼓勵<br />\n咁又有人可能會話，d冇份示威既入黎拎鳩哂點算？<br />\n咁如果佢真係著哂黑衫帶哂口罩帶哂鏡咁入黎為左一張餐卷，咁我都冇野好講<br />\n已經將呢個可能性降至最低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經有出去問過唔少餐廳<br />\n有餐廳就支持，有餐廳聽到叫我死撚開唔好搞咁多野拿拿臨收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個舉動可以拉攏埋餐廳，製造一個同聲同氣既環境比示威者食飯，加大士氣。始終經過左咁耐既拉鋸戰，大家都身心俱疲<br />\n民以食為天，唔想一眾示威者為左食而煩惱，特別係學生，甚至有機會可以令更多學生出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n計劃籌備當中，多人支持眾籌，搞得成就會開始印餐卷同聯絡餐廳安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果真係搞得掂，之後餐卷又派唔哂既，餘下既錢就會用黎買裝備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08145e4c854525a23aeac06bb79f55b8070c9b23","tid":1384911,"uid":274452,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:26:41.000Z","msg":"拎住餐卷去食會冇咁唔好意思<br />\n始終比人請食飯會有一種虧欠感<br />\n<br />\n你地要食飯食肉呀，咁先有力有氣"},{"pid":"c5a587de1dcfd8cba370883461a6c0a99367e5c8","tid":1384911,"uid":241844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:27:44.000Z","msg":"增值左既8達通好啊"},{"pid":"c9b087caa07b4e0466b75d6c2d77bd6ce3542547","tid":1384911,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42ae25afd6d7af21548fadf74443ba1fbb5a578b","tid":1384911,"uid":274452,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"c5a587de1dcfd8cba370883461a6c0a99367e5c8","tid":1384911,"uid":241844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:27:44.000Z","msg":"增值左既8達通好啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:25:01.000Z","msg":"因為八通達好多小店都唔收<br />\n但反而更多本土小店先係支持示威者<br />\n所以增值八達通未必係最有效益<br />\n加上八達通有手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要比佢賺。成本提高左"},{"pid":"c81e684d6e25eae1377cebe3375f1a4167aa0d41","tid":1384911,"uid":274452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:26:34.000Z","msg":"輕推"},{"pid":"ce44f1b8c01c64ea25e27cc50490af3347883506","tid":1384911,"uid":181035,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c5a587de1dcfd8cba370883461a6c0a99367e5c8","tid":1384911,"uid":241844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:27:44.000Z","msg":"增值左既8達通好啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:38:31.000Z","msg":"八達通不了 有機會被追蹤"},{"pid":"2d967d93e2f406307c977ab107c980aad665a07f","tid":1384911,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"最怕有便衣狗餐廳設伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f896c8a85edc6be71da04bed776c7386e8ccceb","tid":1384911,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:46:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>8月5日全港大罷工</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"37a94fdf022669886034f8f9ae85e6ccb95ea3be","tid":1384911,"uid":276013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:47:02.000Z","msg":"其實而家好多家長都開始會買防具俾前線 不如調番轉嗌冇錢學生哥留黎開飯仲好 又唔洗怕尷尬拎卷"},{"pid":"84edf13d305034c87eac6ba01a15d245b5673bf2","tid":1384911,"uid":274452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d967d93e2f406307c977ab107c980aad665a07f","tid":1384911,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"最怕有便衣狗餐廳設伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:56:27.000Z","msg":"咁又唔會<br />\n反而比到壓力比黑警<br />\n擺明就係唔做你生意<br />\n同埋又唔好諗到太白色恐怖"},{"pid":"afe704beeaa4857031cf3dba2d5fc1c7ae8f6569","tid":1384911,"uid":274452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37a94fdf022669886034f8f9ae85e6ccb95ea3be","tid":1384911,"uid":276013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:47:02.000Z","msg":"其實而家好多家長都開始會買防具俾前線 不如調番轉嗌冇錢學生哥留黎開飯仲好 又唔洗怕尷尬拎卷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:57:37.000Z","msg":"拎卷應該唔尷尬掛，個陣個個都黑衫黑口罩<br />\n同埋好撚多家庭都係父母都係藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學生邊敢出聲"},{"pid":"14c6186b6f7fed220ffabbd7a1247433c515ed68","tid":1384911,"uid":274452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f896c8a85edc6be71da04bed776c7386e8ccceb","tid":1384911,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:46:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>8月5日全港大罷工</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5599deedb8ad80b5a4d1d7b6e9dd5cbe1bcdfe","tid":1384911,"uid":184540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:58:37.000Z","msg":"list番邊啲藍餐廳<br />\n唔會再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0175f01dab33295b756cf83b8a431d2b52575dc","tid":1384911,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d967d93e2f406307c977ab107c980aad665a07f","tid":1384911,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"最怕有便衣狗餐廳設伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:02:34.000Z","msg":"用飯券頂多只係證明呢個人係示威現場出現過<br />\n但佢無辦法用呢樣野證明呢個人係和理非定勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0403378a941f9411350d17467ac3532b415413","tid":1384911,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0175f01dab33295b756cf83b8a431d2b52575dc","tid":1384911,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d967d93e2f406307c977ab107c980aad665a07f","tid":1384911,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"最怕有便衣狗餐廳設伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:02:34.000Z","msg":"用飯券頂多只係證明呢個人係示威現場出現過<br />\n但佢無辦法用呢樣野證明呢個人係和理非定勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:08:51.000Z","msg":"出現過都已經唔得<br />\n不過邊個證明到有飯券就係出現過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔好放鬆亂講野就得"},{"pid":"65044bfc685855e81d3893a78ff526f68b45c30e","tid":1384911,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:12:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b7d1ecf641b0f11d66a86f56343b76aa16fb24f","tid":1384911,"uid":22121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:15:05.000Z","msg":"支持，留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1de4aa7849deaf30a0f675a1f925e1f95f2d2f","tid":1384911,"uid":264077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:26:24.000Z","msg":"餐廳啲卷唔單止會淨係派比學生<br />\n仲係同公開發售一模一樣<br />\n唔好因為張卷就會證明學生有參加個活動"},{"pid":"4a723cba81392209dcca254b6779711b0f4ad4b6","tid":1384911,"uid":237175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:28:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7aeae59631e688c5b48bbead8f6c1c2d8131b1d","tid":1384911,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:29:07.000Z","msg":"同意 <br />\nconfirm咗既餐廳可以整個list <br />\n等老豆老母買飯俾仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要只推 , 試著說 「罷工要配合埋 不合作運動 事半功倍」<br />\n<br />\n和理非 站出來 我地去集會遊街不合作運動 等前線休息下<br />\n<br />\n香港人 唔好放棄!<br />\n__________________<br />\n<br />\n*7月30 : 地鐵不合作運動 <br />\n*8月2 : 公務員罷工集會<br />\n*8月5 : 一齊罷工 7區集會 <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">返工放工幫手air drop</span><br />\n停止前線義士受傷被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我要真普選 不要空降假特首</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">先生/小姐，我而家跟據警察通例 Police General Orders 第20章 第14條要求你出示委任證，麻煩請你合作。<br />\n如果你無法出示委任證，根據香港法例第228章 第22條，我有合理理由懷疑你干犯假冒公職人員罪。<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"faaf0bee6c3f3ef30a67c2a4f4cd7e888fda4331","tid":1384911,"uid":258340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8f796a1533776f9476335ef10c008ced5ef540","tid":1384911,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:31:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2979f5dcac241d1765979bac642abc363a717a59","tid":1384911,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:32:56.000Z","msg":"8月5日大罷工!!!"},{"pid":"67680c0dc382f71cb521f9675b58a6dfa8334985","tid":1384911,"uid":207514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:35:24.000Z","msg":"push"}]}